data.description: Cozy little manufactured home sitting on 1.02 acres in sought after La Vernia school district.  With a little TLC, this cute 3 bed/2 bath home is perfect for first time home buyers.  Offers a front porch, back deck where previous above ground pool use to sit, with a large concrete slab for a basketball hoop, or outdoor entertaining potential.  The land shares several mature oak trees for shade and a playscape to sit under.  Such a beautiful landscape to start calling home. Don't miss out on this opportunity of a lifetime, definitely a must see!  Sellers are motivated and willing to offer concessions to help with closing costs and/or fixes, but home is being sold AS-IS.  Will not fix any issues.   Note: Home is vacant but owners are still in the process of moving out.  All furniture will be removed before closing.
